phrases: Do you also feel a stirring in your heart?
And I shall give no quarter to any who would oppose me.
What are you doing in this world?!
Coco, you are that girl from Edolas, right?
You must have come to Earthland while we were gone!
Considering all that, you look pretty young...
What the hell is going on here, Coco?!
Please do not talk so familiarly to me.
This is my first time meeting you people.
That is not what is going on!
I wonder where Gajeel-san went off to...
A Man does not flee from his enemy!
I mean, how did you get to Earthland?!
It seems like they are totally mistaking us for other people!
Let us hurry up and get to work, Sugar Boy-san.
The guys we fought at that royal amusement park!
Now that you mention it, the face is similar...
What are you dressed like a woman for?!
What have you come here for?
You are a pitiful bunch of wizards.
We have got just one demand.
This is my first time seeing a marriage proposal...
That is not what this is!
There is no point in hiding her.
We know Lucy Heartfilia belongs to this guild.
Maybe we would better introduce ourselves, baby!
Why are they after you, Nee-san?
You suddenly show up out of nowhere and make this ridiculous demand?!
You tell me to give you one of my people without so much as a reason,
you cannot seriously expect me to say, Oh, of course.
I do not know who you people are, but get the hell outta here now!
Recently, several churches have been attacked.
Even without positive proof, the timing is too convenient.
I mean, that is a spicy accusation...
We are not obliged to stand here and listen to your drivel.
Just give us Lucy Heartfilia immediately!
But if you refuse to cooperate...
Yes, the springtime of our lives!
Please take care of these two-bit wizards!
That is just gross, in more ways than one!
I do not know what to grab on to!
This stuff is going to do something!
The taste of wizards is spicy!
A long time ago, the three of us
used to sleep in the same bed together like this...
This is no time for nostalgia!
That mucus stuff has a will of its own?!
You said you were the guild's master, right?
Give her to us before people start getting hurt!
I have no interest in hitting kids!
I told you to call me Master!
No way an attack like that is going to hit me!
The building's fallin' apart as it is!
It is all we can do just to hold it off!
It keeps getting bigger and bigger!
Do not tell me the damage from his duel with Laxus finally kicked in?!
I guess it just goes to show that guild wizards are no big deal.
Nothing saddened Coco more than hurting people.
They are not the people we know from Edolas!
Then they are the Coco, Hughes, and Sugar Boy who were already in Earthland!
Just like there were doubles of us in Edolas...
If you do not hurry up and identify yourself,
we are going to put more of the hurt on your friends!
Unless you want us to keep going on a rampage...?
You have got to hold back...
They do not know who Lucy is yet...
You three get outta here and look for Gramps.
You can barely stand up, Natsu!
That is what you get, wizards!
Now dance some more for our amusement!
It seems that girl is not a wizard...
She hit me with a rock...
I have totally got murder on my mind...
Wing Slash of the Sky Dragon!
It is because of that stick!
Since it is come to this, I have no choice
but to call on my Celestial Spirits and fight...
Wish I could use Fleuve d'etoiles that I got from Virgo,
but it will not work for some reason...
Why do I feel so exhausted...?
Maybe it is because of that mucus stuff from before...
I have got no physical strength or magic power...
That stuff sapped it out of us...?
What do you want with Lucy?!
We do not have to answer you!
We will give you five more seconds.
I am the one you are looking for.
What is it that you want with me?
Despite being a guild wizard, she is definitely the daughter
of the former owner of the Heartfilia Konzern.
I figured she would be rougher around the edges...
The daughter of the former owner of the Heartfilia Konzern
and Fairy Tail's resident Celestial Spirit wizard...
Now that they mention it, she sure looks like she fits the bill...
I am touched that you are trying to protect me.
But I do not think your lie would work anyway!
And even if they did believe it, they would see through your guise soon enough!
I cannot because anyone more trouble than I already have!
Let us tell them the truth!
So that girl is trying to protect Lucy, huh?
Well, we know the real thing is over 20 years old,
so the girl with the pigtails is too young to be her, right?
That is because we were on Tenroujima for seven years...
I will not let'them lay one finger on you!
You still have some fight in you, do not you, Lucy?
I do not know which is the real one!
So we should just round'them all up?
Dazzling Blaze of the Fire Dragon!
Let us hurry, while those three are distracted!
Not if we have anything to say about it!
It was banned after so many people got injured from it.
Not one of my hound dogs' favorites...
But they have got good chemistry with you.
In what month where you born?
For now, let us look for the Master around here...
But why did you say you were Lucy?!
W-Well, I thought you were in danger, so on impulse, I...
I am a Celestial Spirit wizard, so even if they had captured me,
I would have been able to escape one way or another.
But if they would gotten their hands on you, who cannot use any magic...
I had not thought about what would happen after...
I cannot use magic, so I thought I could at least help that way...
You know, you really have a risky side...
Come to think of it, I may have been the same way
when I first joined the guild...
I would act rashly again and again...
From now on, though, I have really got to keep it together.
By the way, I wonder why those guys are after me...
Kinana-san thought they might be the criminals who raided those churches...
But I do not have anything to do with any church...
And I am not letting you get away again!
You are scary in a plain way!
Sorry, sorry, I was lying before.
Actually, this girl is the real Lucy-chan!
This one is the real deal!
This is the one and only Lucy-san!
Real Lucy-chan, lying to save your bacon from getting caught is not right!
You know you are the genuine article!
In fact, the truth is that I was just lying now too,
so I actually am the real, true blue you-know-who!
But really, the real, true, actual, factual person
you are after is me after all!
I know this is sudden, but I am the genuine princess.
What did you suddenly come out for?!
I thought I would give you a hand, Princess.
You are correct, but I am the true princess.
But you know, I may be Lucy after all...
I may be the real Lucy...
That went well, did not it, Princess?
I feel really guilty about doing that to her...
It seems one of the two that Coco chased after is the real Lucy Heartfilia.
I see you can change your mode too, kitty-cat.
It is totally hard to fight like this!
All of you, just fight for cryin' out loud!
Mary Hughes, our time here is limited.
I say we go after Lucy, too!
I can tame several people at once with my Command Magic!
These creeps are tough customers, huh?
Where the hell did Gajeel go?
Everyone is probably back at the guild by now.
I wanted us to find him, for Levy's sake, too...
I guess we can go out looking again tomorrow...
I know they are out looking for the Master,
but I do not know where they are looking!
For some reason, I cannot detect any trace of Lucy-san...
Bastards... Treatin' me like a smoke bomb...
So Natsu and the others went in search of Lu-chan.
I got caught up in the fight...
Just the three of them made all of us look like fools.
This is no time to give out scores!
I lost sight of Lucy Heartfilia.
Hey, Natsu, do not you know Lucy's scent?
It is like getting mixed up with another scent...
Maybe it is that thing's fault...?
My hound dogs said they want to play with you some more!
I will make'them look like a puddle of snail slime
Whether it is food or people, I hate things that are sweet!
Even though your name is Sugar Boy?!
It is no good if you see what is right in front of you,
but lose sight of the main subject.
You were so kind to give it to me, but...
I suspect the because is being in suspended animation
for seven years, but I will take it back
to the Celestial Spirit World and try repairing it.
So this is Celestial Spirit Magic...
Uh-huh, and there are a lot more than just Plue and Virgo!
Like the goat, Aquarius, and the crab?
The exact route that Samuel figured you would take beforehand...
My feet are moving by themselves...
You will fall off the cliff!
My legs are not listening to me!
I thought you were going to take the both of us!
If you suffer a serious injury, there is no chance you will escape again!
At this rate, you will fall with me, Nee-san!
I believe we will have her very soon, Byro-sama.
That bastard who sucked the magic power out of me and Wendy?!
He is totally different from the Edolas Byro!
Byro-sama is standing on top of the octopus!
We have come to capture the Heartfilia girl.
Swiftly dispose of those who stand in our way and return to the main mission.
That saves me the trouble of having to control both of you!
Yeah, well, if I get serious, they will be a walk in the park!
Then why have not you gotten serious?
It is cooler if I wait'til everyone is in a pinch,
then I swoop in and kick the bad guys' asses!
That is what you say, but I bet you are already fighting seriously
and still having a hard time!
Next time: The Fury of Legion!
S-Seriously, it will be an easy win!
I think it will be easier on you if you are honest...
Do not you look at me with sympathetic eyes!
